Products.RichDescription:
MAGNUM LUXE ICE CREAM GOLD CARAMELISED CHOCOLATE 440 ML

Magnum LUXE is the first super premium ice cream, positioned at the top of the range of indulgent ice cream sticks and tubs - a permissable luxury
Our Magnum LUXE range heroes sauce - this is what differentiates it from the core. Each stick & pints has a delicious, luscious sauce, elevating the indulgent Magnum experience. Each of the flavors are also extremely decadent, have you already tried Raspberry Panna Cotta sticks and Salted Caramel pint?
For the first time, the Magnum LUXE range features layers of velvety ice cream, luscious sauces and thick chocolate, paired together for the perfect balance to transport you to experience an indulgent moment of pleasure.
This Magnum is a true authentic pleasure, so good it’s worth letting go for. When indulging in Magnum LUXE you should feel as though you are having an extra special treat and spoiling yourself!

Magnum cocoa (chocolate) beans are high quality ingredients and have a long way to go before they become Magnum chocolate. We’re working closely with the Rainforest Alliance to make sure all our cocoa beans are responsibly sourced (and delicious, of course!). It’s about quality and sustainability throughout every step of the journey. Since 1989, Pleasure Seekers around the world have been discovering Magnum icecream, and we have been taking pleasure very seriously. Thick Chocolate. Smooth ice cream. The perfect balance. To us, pleasure is everything. The pleasure of each individual and their freedom to experience it genuinely and in full. We know pleasure can be found in both the smallest and the biggest things. Can be a treat, a stick, a tub, a bar, a snack, a dessert. But only if you are brave enough will you really find your pleasure, your true pleasure that stays with you. We are Magnum ice cream, the champions of true pleasure.

Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream and frozen dessert is made from our highest quality cocoa beans, sustainably grown and carefully selected by Rainforest Alliance Certified™ farmers.

Store at -18°C. Remove from the freezer 5-10 minutes before consuming it.

Magnum LUXE, the most decadent and indulgent Magnum range yet. Magnum believes that a day without pleasure is a day lost & pleasure makes life worth living.

Indulge in white chocolate ice cream, dipped in chocolate compound, dipped in a butter caramely sauce and coated in thick, cracking gold caramelised Magnum chocolate with vanilla biscuits inclusions. Pure pleasure.

With Magnum LUXE, Pleasure has more than one layer. When I want a moment of indulging myself, I want the most exciting and indulgent things to feel EXTRA special.

Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream is certified by Rainforest Alliance in any flavour. Magnum sticks are a delicious treat for every family.

Magnum chocolate dessert icecream is made from our highest quality cocoa beans, sustainably grown and carefully selected to deliver the best chocolate flavours to you.

Every Magnum stick, tub or bar is made with high quality ingrediants to give you and your family a delicious frozen dessert or ice cream that can be consumed as a snack or a treat any moment of the day.
